title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 16 §§ 892-3.9 - Severability
content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 16 §§ 892-3.9 - Severability

State Regulations

If any provision of this Subpart or the application of
such provision to any circumstances is held invalid for any reason whatsoever, the remainder of this Subpart or the application of the provision to other
circumstances shall not be affected thereby. Notes
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 16
§§
892-3.9

State regulations are updated quarterly; we currently have two versions available. Below is a
comparison between our most recent version and the prior quarterly release. More comparison features will be added as we have more versions to compare. No prior version found.
